languages.text: "Я видела его после того, как Лорд-капитан удалил{mf|ся|ась} в свои покои. Бедняга держался за голову и явно был немного не в себе. А вот почему... это мне уже неведомо".
"I saw him after the Lord Captain retired to {mf|his|her} chambers. The poor man was clutching his head and was clearly a little out of sorts. As to the reason why... I have no idea."

languages.text: “舰长大人回房休息之后，我见过他一面。那个可怜的人一直紧紧抱着自己的头，显然有点不太舒服。至于为什么会这样……我就不知道了。”
languages.original_text: "I saw him after the Lord Captain retired to {mf|his|her} chambers. The poor man was clutching his head and was clearly a little out of sorts. As to the reason why... I have no idea."

languages.text: « Je l'ai vu peu après que {mf|le seigneur-capitaine|la seigneure-capitaine} s'est {mf|retiré|retirée} dans ses quartiers. Le pauvre homme se tenait la tête à deux mains et n'était clairement pas dans son assiette. Quant à savoir pourquoi... Je n'en ai pas la moindre idée. »
languages.original_text: "I saw him after the Lord Captain retired to {mf|his|her} chambers. The poor man was clutching his head and was clearly a little out of sorts. As to the reason why... I have no idea."

languages.text: «Le vi después de que {mf|el|la} Lord Capitán se retirara a sus aposentos. El pobre diablo se sujetaba la cabeza y estaba un poco descolocado... Ni idea de por qué».

languages.text: 「ソイツならロード・キャプテンが自室に戻った後に見かけたよ。かわいそうだね、頭を抱えて、どう見ても少し気分が悪そうだった。理由は…アタシにはわからないけど」

languages.text: "Ich habe ihn gesehen, nachdem der Lord Captain sich zurückgezogen hatte. Der arme Mann hat sich den Kopf gehalten und war offenkundig nicht ganz bei sich. Warum allerdings ... Das weiß ich nicht."
languages.original_text: "I saw him after the Lord Captain retired to {mf|his|her} chambers. The poor man was clutching his head and was clearly a little out of sorts. As to the reason why... I have no idea."

languages.text: "Onu Lord Kaptan odasına çekildikten sonra gördüm. Zavallı adamcağız kafasını tutuyordu, keyifsiz olduğu belliydi. Nedenine gelirsek... Hiçbir fikrim yok."
